    "description": "<br><br><strong>Edemn</strong>是一款有趣的动态射击游戏，讲述了通过古代魔法崛起的骷髅，现在他们之间的战斗。游戏采用了21世纪初的游戏风格，创造了一种很酷的游戏氛围。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219660/extras/a80569a8d3a173abdf0c1079227ab958.poster.avif?t=1687378097\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219660/extras/a80569a8d3a173abdf0c1079227ab958.webm?t=1687378097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219660/extras/a80569a8d3a173abdf0c1079227ab958.mp4?t=1687378097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219660/extras/bd1bebf7bed7ad5552522f99883f8d17.webp?t=1687378097\" width=600 height=56 /></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219660/extras/cf5fe5a38bdccacb71e1d226c6e582d9.webp?t=1687378097\" width=600 height=56 /></span> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Edemn的每场比赛都会有变化，而且会拖得很久。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219660/extras/4bc4da2b3fae14f52cc67d7b42690817.poster.avif?t=1687378097\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219660/extras/4bc4da2b3fae14f52cc67d7b42690817.webm?t=1687378097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219660/extras/4bc4da2b3fae14f52cc67d7b42690817.mp4?t=1687378097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219660/extras/e35e1758bb8269fab976aa88f28bc0dc.webp?t=1687378097\" width=600 height=56 /></span> <br>[列表]</li><li>皮肤，每一个都是独一无二的，将使你的游戏和你的角色的外观多样化[/列表] 。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219660/extras/skin_show.gif ?t=1687378097\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219660/extras/6444c5d099761b542651e5df5347e47b.webp?t=1687378097\" width=600 height=56 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>每个皮肤都是独一无二的，每个皮肤都有自己独特的能力，在战斗中会有这样或那样的帮助</li></ul> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219660/extras/d7cd1c3fa2931ea2ccbf46cf6e39fd23.poster.avif?t=1687378097\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219660/extras/d7cd1c3fa2931ea2ccbf46cf6e39fd23.webm?t=1687378097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219660/extras/d7cd1c3fa2931ea2ccbf46cf6e39fd23.mp4?t=1687378097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219660/extras/cc428a990d3c36a6e2f92d1e5ca17431.webp?t=1687378097\" width=600 height=56 /></span> <br>[列表]</li><li>Edemn将增加新的模式。<br>在目前可用的模式中，是Deathmatсh</li></ul><br>",
